title: We Finally Have the Stranger Things Season 2 Premiere Date!
text:
Stranger Things Season 2 Release Date We Finally Have the Stranger Things Season 2 Premiere Date! February 5, 2017 by Shannon Vestal Robson 190 Shares 
Start your countdown clocks for Halloween 2017! That's when Stranger Things season two is coming back, as revealed by the Super Bowl teaser ad revealed during the big game. That's quite a long way to go, considering season one debuted in July of 2016, but it couldn't be more perfect to return on the spookiest night of the year. So, while you wait, read up on what we do know about season two , like the new cast members and when it will be set !
